text: Allison is a city in Iowa in the United States. It was named for U.S. Senator William Boyd Allison. As of 2020, 966 people live in Allison.https://www2.census.gov/programs- surveys/decennial/2020/data/01-Redistricting_File--PL_94-171/Iowa/ ==References== Category:Cities in Iowa Category:County seats in Iowa
